init_text: All of the "#1 Dad" mugs in the world change to show the actual ranking of Dads suddenly.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: All the dads now have a chip on their shoulder and feel they need to step up their game.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: There are now more dads making family dinners, helping with homework, taking the little league team to practice, and even running in marath

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They know if they start slacking, the mug will rank them lowly.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They are forced to be the best dads they can be.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She felt her mission was complete and the world was now a better place.
